<p>Lea is a front-end web developer located in Greece. She is passionate about JavaScript and CSS3 and shares her love for Web Standards at various events around the world (including the prestigious SXSW, Web Directions @media, Fronteers, JSConfEU, and Frontend) and through her blog, <a href="http://lea.verou.me/">lea.verou.me</a>. Lea is a contributor to publications such as <a href="http://www.netmagazine.com/">.net Magazine</a>, <a href="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/">Smashing Magazine</a>, and <a href="http://24ways.org/">24ways</a>, and the creator of <a href="http://lea.verou.me/css3-tools/">famous web applications</a> that demonstrate the possibilities of CSS3.</p>
<p>Lea also tweets <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/leaverou">@LeaVerou</a>.</p>
